(41, 3, 12, 40, 8, 4, 4, 'that they should not make him known', 'Jesus'' Command for Silence', 'This connection highlights Jesus'' instruction to keep his identity concealed. Both passages emphasize the directive to not make him known.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
