(41, 3, 14, 44, 1, 8, 8, 'that he might send them forth', 'Commissioning of Witnesses', 'This connection highlights the theme of being sent forth to preach and witness. Both passages emphasize the call to spread the message of Jesus, first through the twelve apostles and later through the empowered believers.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
