(41, 3, 14, 43, 15, 16, 16, 'that they should be with him', 'Chosen and Ordained for Mission', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of being chosen and ordained for a specific purpose. In Mark, the twelve are ordained to preach, while in John, Jesus states he has chosen and ordained his followers to bear fruit.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
